losopher who is spiritual, literary, and rigorous all at once – both a brilliant controversialist and a thinker of substance.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aPhilosophical theology. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Religious.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978144268699140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781442686991423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781442686991.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK